title: Royal Enfield Hunter 350
description: Royal Enfield Bullet 350 is a cruiser bike available at a starting price of Rs. 1,50,893 in India. It is available in 3 variants and 6 colours with top variant price starting from Rs. 1,66,042. The Royal Enfield Bullet 350 is powered by 346cc BS6 engine which develops a power of 19.1 bhp and a torque of 28 Nm. With front disc and rear drum brakes, Royal Enfield Bullet 350 comes up with anti-locking braking system. This Bullet 350 bike weighs 191 kg and has a fuel tank
